{"tid":1286865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我有嘢講] 理性討論七七遊行目標","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T08:50:43.000Z","uid":263659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a4793b03db8ef493c65fbe0d6acde9277d9f928e","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"關於七七遊行嘅目標見到大家開始有分歧， 甚至有人話如果有人講武漢就拉隊走。但七七其實好重要，同埋素人搞遊行號召力已經冇咁高，真係要有幾多出幾多。所以想大家討論吓，試吓搵個共識。遊行都要一齊行！<br />\n<br />\n目標一：向林鄭繼續施壓，堅持不撤不散<br />\n目標二：向遊客 (特別係大陸嘅) 宣傳香港反送中嘅事<br />\n目標三：向大陸遊客宣傳遊行抗議「維權」嘅意識，令北京頭痛<br />\n目標四：聲援武昌起義<br />\n=============================================<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標一：向林鄭繼續施壓，堅持不撤不散</span></strong><br />\n冇爭議<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>但若只做目標一，遊行去西九意義冇咁大</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而若果做埋其他，又怕運動失焦</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標二：向遊客 (特別係大陸嘅) 宣傳香港反送中嘅事</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>好處就係擴大戰線，和理非上嘅某程度升級</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但若果目標群眾係大陸人，只講香港、民主呢啲佢哋WFC</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標三：向大陸遊客宣傳遊行抗議「維權」嘅意識，令北京頭痛</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>同樣係擴大戰線，要搵啲佢哋有共鳴嘅，輸出革命，爭取更大籌碼</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但會偏離五大訴求，北京頭痛之餘我哋自己都頭痕</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標四：聲援武昌起義</span></strong><br />\n香港大陸社運連線，最有爭議<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">武漢示威者唔係反共，但當抗議持續，訴求冇人聽仲要被打壓，仲堅持嘅人反對嘅層面只會愈嚟愈高。反送中69、612、甚至616都未有人嗌雙普選，626民陣話重啟政改我記得都有人鬧失焦，依家就好似有咗共識。所以<strong>依家未反共，唔代表之後唔會意識到問題根源其實都係共產黨，會有共同敵人，拉一派打一派</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但有機會嚴重失焦，訴求上升到呢個層次本地政府都唔會有辦法滿足到，變相放生林鄭</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n=============================================<br />\n最後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqW3bQA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqW3bQA.gif&h=8589a4c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09d0a1603fda6966a56a64bffef78c5c70fc5378","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f4d1ae2139755382832bddabed50a09d1cd8b8fb","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"d08e05f06a417fd7bc99b37c49ed789e3c8c609e","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"我唔解鎖"},{"pid":"0188f1a634c5847932caf68f4d5d5d862839e971","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"我唔簽野"},{"pid":"32c25bd35bac8a9de0593854f3bc5dce1e0a6759","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"唔好兇我"},{"pid":"5be1eae58871a77694126302a6cd29f4e212f61b","tid":1286865,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae980cf24df2897433626847a9450c2bb160a532","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"我要食飯"},{"pid":"35c7c04c9c95c08d0521f25b86ad8ded51192ca7","tid":1286865,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"我要飲水"},{"